OL,3,CSchool children to be taught value of
OL,4,Carmed forces under new government plans
OL,6,FChildren in Britain will be taught
OL,7,Fabout the importance of the armed
OL,8,Fforces in school under new government
OL,9,Fplans.
OL,11,FThe proposal, first reported by the
OL,12,FTelegraph, is part of the government's
OL,13,Fstrategic defence review which is due
OL,14,Fto be published on Monday.
