OL,3,CSchool children to be taught value of
OL,4,Carmed forces under new government plans
OL,6,FIt will recommend that state school
OL,7,Fstudents should be taught the value of
OL,8,Fthe military, to help young people
OL,9,Flearn about careers in defence, and to
OL,10,Fboost their connection with the armed
OL,11,Fforces in an increasingly insecure
OL,12,Fworld.
OL,14,FThe plans include a suggestion army
OL,15,Freservists could visit schools and
OL,16,Fspeak to children about working in the
OL,17,Fmilitary.
