OL,6,FThe strategic defence review was
OL,7,Flaunched by the Labour government
OL,8,Fshortly after the election, designed
OL,9,Fto usher in a "new era for defence" in
OL,10,Fan time of global instability.
OL,12,FThe prime minister announced in
OL,13,FFebruary that the UK would increase
OL,14,Fdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP by
OL,15,F2027, funded by a cut in the overseas
OL,16,Faid budget.
