OL,3,CSchool children to be taught value of
OL,4,Carmed forces under new government plans
OL,6,FAs ITV News Political Correspondent
OL,7,FCarl Dinnen reported last week, the
OL,8,Freview will call for much greater
OL,9,Finvestment in hi-tech weaponry,
OL,10,Fparticularly drone and anti-drone
OL,11,Fsystems, a shift that is already
OL,12,Funderway as a result of the war in
OL,13,FUkraine.
OL,15,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD)
OL,16,Fannounced this week they will spend
OL,17,Fover # 1 billion on AI and drone
OL,18,Ftechnology to speed up decisions on
OL,19,Fthe battlefield.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
