OL,3,CSchool children to be taught value of
OL,4,Carmed forces under new government plans
OL,6,FSome commitments - such as the nuclear
OL,7,Fdeterrent, NATO membership and support
OL,8,Ffor Ukraine - are baked into the
OL,9,Freview's parameters.
OL,11,FThe reviewers have also been asked to
OL,12,Flook at how to reinforce UK homeland
OL,13,Fsecurity with reports that a civilian
OL,14,F'Home Guard', separate from the
OL,15,FReserves, will be among the
OL,16,Frecommendations.
