OL,6,FUnusually for a defence review, the
OL,7,Fkey work has been done independently
OL,8,Fof the Ministry of Defence by the
OL,9,Fformer NATO Secretary-General and
OL,10,FDefence Secretary Lord Robertson,
OL,11,Fformer Deputy Chief of the Defence
OL,12,FStaff General Sir Richard Barrons, and
OL,13,FDr Fiona Hill, who advised Donald
OL,14,FTrump on European and Russian affairs
OL,15,Fduring his first term.
